data.description:
Near Lake Belton with Lake Views!! This Almost 3/4 Acre Lot is 4 bedroom 3 Bathroom with a pool home nestled in the hills of Belton!! As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the expansive layout with high ceilings. Clean lines and Crown Molding are abundant with natural light to create an inviting ambiance, perfect for both relaxation and entertainment. Huge Primary Bedroom with Retreat and Lake Views Downstairs. Primary Closet is the size of a small bedroom!! Private Office on the other side of the house is perfect for privacy and quiet!

Enjoy spacious formal dining and eat in kitchen areas with MORE Lake Views!! A kitchen equipped with upgraded appliances, quartz countertops, and ample storage. Additional 2 Bedrooms, full bath and loft upstairs, this is a well laid out floor plan!

The backyard consists of a covered patio and landscaped yard, offering outdoor enjoyment. Plenty of space in the front of the house for boats, toys, continued outdoor living!!  This property has been very well cared for, extremely clean and priced to sell!! 8 miles to downtown Belton.
